sacrifice corpse

requires: black liquid (not used)

trace a crude replication of the circle w/ the black liquid
prick finger and dab blood onto the symbols (10 hp)
place hand on circle
shadows pour from the symbols into your hand
corpse is replaced with a husk that dests in 20 seconds

if corpse level < 20 THEN timer +gets 1/2 corpse level
if corpse level < 25 THEN timer +gets corpse level
if corpse level > 24 THEN timer +gets corpse level * 2
  if timer
   msg in hb:  shadows swirl around your fist
   if end < max, end++, timer--
   if sp < max, sp++, timer--
  hp--
   if blast & timer, bonus hit_player() of timer dmg, costs 1/2 timer sps, 5 endurance


look at fist for level of charge
